<p>Greenlight: Possibly</p>
<p>Page type: Scp Article</p>
<p>Genre: Fantasy</p>
<p>Elevator pitch: The bad omen man is an unfortunate anomaly that seems to break everything around him against his will. He is kind and witty, but with a short temper.</p>
<p>Central Narrative: The bad omen man is a tall black humanoid, with their facial structure resembling a bat. When bored the structures around them accelerate deterioration by about 10 fold, resulting in poor foundation and containment breaches. When upset, things tend to happen like breaches with no logic of how it could have happened, sudden personnel death, and in one case, the detonation of the internals of a generator causing a site-wide blackout and breaches. This is not restricted to any radius around him, happening all over the world, and even on other planets, and close realities. Fortunately, if given time, he will bond with personnel. He enjoys video games, board games, and honestly is a very polite and kind individual, despite his short temper.</p>
<p>Hook/Attention getter: Entertainment is a good thing, but sometimes it's the most important thing.</p>

